{"tid":588470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[習帝永續]人大2958票通過","createTime":"2018-03-11T08:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T15:33:47.000Z","uid":111669,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1c9303e95b52ab989d5406ed3d48c8af766094","tid":588470,"uid":111669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報:<br />\n<br />\n正在北京舉行的全國人大會議，下午舉行第三次全體會議，投票表決憲法修正案草案。以2958票贊成、2票反對、3票棄權通過，另有1張無效票，意味着刪除國家主席任期限制、讓習近平可以無限連任的條文獲得通過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習帝好多支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國世界第一 專出無賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4b569e1796bacbec4dcb2d5a64fcd75a4b499d","tid":588470,"uid":27813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"2票反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2ffe9c1117340f5e07ad12cb78ff758f9b99dc","tid":588470,"uid":52614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"登基啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe803dafd91ae359aa2b0990345fac2e871af2ff","tid":588470,"uid":12158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca4b569e1796bacbec4dcb2d5a64fcd75a4b499d","tid":588470,"uid":27813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"2票反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"兩票反對，咪同香港啲泛民一樣，扮下嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f784d5607044ee0686a17b5aeb1658960f92c","tid":588470,"uid":23874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1